# agentic-control Development

## Package Overview

Dual TypeScript/Python package for AI agent management.

## TypeScript Commands

```bash
pnpm install         # Install deps
pnpm run build       # Build with tsc
pnpm run test        # Run vitest tests
pnpm run format      # Format with Prettier
```

## Python Commands

```bash
cd python
uv sync --extra tests
uv run pytest tests/ -v
uvx ruff check --fix src/
uvx ruff format src/
```

## Key Patterns

- TypeScript uses Prettier for formatting
- Python uses Ruff for linting/formatting
- Both support MCP server protocols
- Python requires 3.10+ (crewai)
